The Grand Master of Reality Revisionists, Darvros 
the Magnificent, is having a little trouble finding 
the time to get away to search for some things he
needs for his next grand project. However, he's more 
than willing to accept help from others, and probably 
willing to compensate his helpers as well.

If you'd like to help, just go mention something to 
him about the potion he's working on, and he'll give 
you the details.

Darvros, by the way, is the guild master of the Reality 
Revisionists. He keeps shop just outside the town of 
Glaverton, far from the depradations of the demons that 
have invaded Glavia.

This is a lower level quest.
